#: ../../source/unit/miniscale.rst:2 82b1882517df4acfab97220e795da950
msgid "Miniscale Unit"
msgstr "Miniscale Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/miniscale.rst:6 1a04b5f2180d4a06bd2d4de9a80340f5
msgid ""
"The ``Miniscale`` class is designed for interfacing with a mini scale "
"weight sensor, which includes a HX711 22-bit ADC. This sensor is capable "
"of measuring weight and also includes additional functionalities like LED"
" control and various filters."
msgstr ""
"``Miniscale`` 类用于与迷你称重传感器进行接口连接，该传感器包含一个 HX711 22-bit "
"ADC。该传感器能够测量重量，并且还包含 LED 控制以及多种滤波等附加功能。"

