msgid ""
"This example demonstrates how to read and display weight values from the "
"MiniScale unit. It sets up an average filter level of 10 for smoother "
"readings and updates the weight display every second."
msgstr "该示例演示如何从 MiniScale unit 读取并显示重量值。它将平均滤波等级设置为 10，以获得更平滑的读数，并每 1 秒更新一次重量显示。"

